Introducing our NEW Creamy Obsession Eyeshadow Palette… in NEUTRAL BROWN!
 
This chocolate-y palette includes 9 dreamy eyeshadows that are oh-so-smooth! From dreamy cream-to-mattes to marbles, metallic shimmers, and staple mattes, it’s the only palette you need to grab on your way out. 😉
 
What’s inside: 
✅ 8 creamy shades + 1 translucent shade to set
✅ SUPER pigmented for that extra WOW factor! 
✅ Super easy to blend, build, layer & love

This Mistake Almost Killed My Company! I CAN’T BELIEVE I’m FINALLY sharing this with the world. I won’t lie... This was hard for me to shoot, but it’s a message I need to share with you all – you DESERVE to know! 

There’s going to be A LOT of changes coming – Huda Beauty is going through a MAJOR shift, but it’s a super exciting time. I’m BACK, and I want to connect with you more than ever and make Huda Beauty THE best it’s ever been! SO stay tuned because 2024 is going to be BIG 💖 #hudabeauty
